I'll have nothing of value to tell you.

67
04:33:33,046 --> 04:33:36,106
<i>Come on, Marty, you're closing</i>
<i>the U/North case. You're settling.</i>

68
04:33:36,283 --> 04:33:40,743
<i>I know that. I know you're up there with</i>
<i>600 people jamming this thing through.</i>

69
04:33:40,921 --> 04:33:43,355
Here's what I know.
Your deadline was 20 minutes ago.

70
04:33:43,524 --> 04:33:47,016
So you're fishing for a story or
trying to get out of writing a retraction.

71
04:33:47,194 --> 04:33:49,685
In either case,
I wish you the best of luck.

72
04:33:50,798 --> 04:33:52,823
Where the fuck is Karen Crowder?

73
