Half the pot. Two hundred.

80
04:34:57,698 --> 04:34:59,393
DEALER:
Two hundred to go.

81
04:35:10,510 --> 04:35:11,772
You don't remember me, huh?

82
04:35:13,146 --> 04:35:15,273
We played together a couple times.

83
04:35:15,449 --> 04:35:17,542
That lamp place on Bowery.

84
04:35:17,718 --> 04:35:20,380
That guy's showroom?
All the lamps and shit?

85
04:35:20,988 --> 04:35:22,956
- The Galaxy.
